<h3 id="create-bucket" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#create-bucket" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Create bucket</h3>
<p>Caution: If this is the first run of your User node, you need to wait about 10~20 minutes for node to complete synchronization. If sync is not complete yet, you will get a &quot;lfs service is read only&quot; error.</p>
<p>After that you can begin create bucket.</p>
